About Doorbell-py
=================

Doorbell-py is free software used for checking whether the lights are on at 
Tinkartank hackerspace <http://tinkartank.org/>. When the lights change state 
the script calls a external script at the server hosting Tinkartanks website.

Written for Raspberry pi using python.

